  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unleash Your Logic And Creativity In This Mind-Bending Machine-Building Adventure.</strong></h2>Axon Hero is more than just a puzzle game - it's a creative playground where logic meets imagination. Build, code, and conquer your way through many hand-crafted challenges, each one more mind-bending than the last.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build Your Factory Masterpiece</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/26e23cb1f21f3b769c17d22ee80d49bc.poster.avif?t=1709173757\" width=600 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/26e23cb1f21f3b769c17d22ee80d49bc.webm?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/26e23cb1f21f3b769c17d22ee80d49bc.mp4?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Design your own intricate factories filled with conveyor belts, splitters, color converters, and more.<br></li><li>Experiment with different machine layouts to find the perfect solution to each unique puzzle.<br></li><li>Watch your creation come to life as boxes navigate your circuit, guided by your logic code.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose From A Wide Range Of Machines</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/3f6b0b27f6332c49cc4d36af2487bcbc.poster.avif?t=1709173757\" width=600 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/3f6b0b27f6332c49cc4d36af2487bcbc.webm?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/3f6b0b27f6332c49cc4d36af2487bcbc.mp4?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Discover a diverse collection of wacky machines, each with its own special function.<br></li><li>Master the art of manipulating boxes, changing their colors, and directing their path.<br></li><li>Combine machines in ingenious ways to overcome increasingly challenging puzzles.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Code Your Own Logic</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/1e5430bee4ac63db129fcdcfc59f5809.poster.avif?t=1709173757\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/1e5430bee4ac63db129fcdcfc59f5809.webm?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/1e5430bee4ac63db129fcdcfc59f5809.mp4?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unleash your inner programmer and code your own custom logic circuits.<br></li><li>Use logic gates like AND, OR, and NOT to control your machines and solve puzzles in unique ways.<br></li><li>No coding experience required - just drag, drop, and connect to bring your genius to life!</li></ul><br><i> Build, Code, Conquer - Axon Hero awaits!</i>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unleash Your Logic And Creativity In This Mind-Bending Machine-Building Adventure.</strong></h2>Axon Hero is more than just a puzzle game - it's a creative playground where logic meets imagination. Build, code, and conquer your way through many hand-crafted challenges, each one more mind-bending than the last.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build Your Factory Masterpiece</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/26e23cb1f21f3b769c17d22ee80d49bc.poster.avif?t=1709173757\" width=600 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/26e23cb1f21f3b769c17d22ee80d49bc.webm?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/26e23cb1f21f3b769c17d22ee80d49bc.mp4?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Design your own intricate factories filled with conveyor belts, splitters, color converters, and more.<br></li><li>Experiment with different machine layouts to find the perfect solution to each unique puzzle.<br></li><li>Watch your creation come to life as boxes navigate your circuit, guided by your logic code.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose From A Wide Range Of Machines</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/3f6b0b27f6332c49cc4d36af2487bcbc.poster.avif?t=1709173757\" width=600 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/3f6b0b27f6332c49cc4d36af2487bcbc.webm?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/3f6b0b27f6332c49cc4d36af2487bcbc.mp4?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Discover a diverse collection of wacky machines, each with its own special function.<br></li><li>Master the art of manipulating boxes, changing their colors, and directing their path.<br></li><li>Combine machines in ingenious ways to overcome increasingly challenging puzzles.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Code Your Own Logic</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/1e5430bee4ac63db129fcdcfc59f5809.poster.avif?t=1709173757\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/1e5430bee4ac63db129fcdcfc59f5809.webm?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/1e5430bee4ac63db129fcdcfc59f5809.mp4?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unleash your inner programmer and code your own custom logic circuits.<br></li><li>Use logic gates like AND, OR, and NOT to control your machines and solve puzzles in unique ways.<br></li><li>No coding experience required - just drag, drop, and connect to bring your genius to life!</li></ul><br><i> Build, Code, Conquer - Axon Hero awaits!</i>",
